description: Reflecting on a year at the Python Software Foundation (PSF), I’ll share insights into how the CPython project and its surrounding efforts, as well as the PSF, operate. Learn how anyone can get involved in areas like code, documentation, or PSF projects, and uncover some lesser-known aspects of the PSF’s inner workings. Discover how you can contribute to—from code to documentation—and help shape Python’s future.
title: One Year In: Insights and Inspiration from my PSF Journey
